          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1648.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p>\n<p>Meanwhile, drain the <strong>tuna</strong></p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong>, <strong>capers</strong>, <strong>roasted </strong><strong>garlic paste</strong> and <strong>drained tuna</strong> to the pan and cook for 30 sec</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1648.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1648.-step-5-x400.jpg",
