          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove the pan from the heat and stir through the<strong> chopped basil</strong> – this is your <strong>tuna, lemon &amp; caper spaghetti </strong></p>\n<p>Cut the <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>remaining</strong></span> <strong>lemon</strong> into wedges</p>",
      "order": 7,
